title: Pluto - 6 Books (gnv64)
description:
A collection of 6 books on Pluto 3 ePUBs & 3 PDFs, also included is the wikipedia article:

1. How I Killed Pluto and Why It Had It Coming (Jan 2012)
   by Mike Brown
  
2. Pluto: New Horizons for a Lost Horizon: Astronomy, Astrology, and Mythology (Mar 2015)
   by Richard Grossinger and Richard C. Hoagland
  
3. Pluto Confidential: An Insider Account of the Ongoing Battles over the Status of Pluto (Aug 2009)
   by Laurence A. Marschall and Stephen P. Maran
  
4. The Case for Pluto: How a Little Planet Made a Big Difference (Nov 2009)
   by Alan Boyle
  
5. The Dwarf Planet Pluto (Space!) (Sept 2009)
   by Kristi Lew
  
6. The Pluto Files: The Rise and Fall of America's Favorite Planet (Sept 2014)
   by Neil deGrasse Tyson
